From d9d40999fa12ad956b8b113d2f5640c72deef454 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mikael Magnusson <mikachu@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 09:31:09 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] potentially handle ctrl-u correctly

---
 chrome/browser/ui/accelerator_table.cc        |  8 +++---
 .../render_widget_host_view_aura.cc           | 25 ++++++++++++++++---
 .../editing/commands/editing_command_type.h   |  2 ++
 .../core/editing/commands/editor_command.cc   | 15 +++++++++++
 .../editing/commands/editor_command_names.h   |  1 +
